<script>
import { Pie, mixins } from "vue-chartjs";

export default {
  extends: Pie,
  mixins: [mixins.reactiveData, mixins.reactiveProp],
  props: ["chartData", "options"],
   watch: {
    chartData () {
      this.renderChart(this.chartData, this.options)
    }
  },
  mounted () {
    this.renderChart(this.chartData, this.options)
  }
};
</script>
